# Python and .NET Core Optimization

- Prioritize backend-only logic; skip frontend-only patterns.
- Detect and classify project stack (`python`, `dotnet`) from structure and files.
- Build prompt context with only relevant stack details to reduce token usage.
- Prefer concise summaries of directory trees and key files over full dumps.
- Cache reusable session context using memory-tree nodes and fingerprints.
- Always produce deterministic prompt sections: rules, skills, structure, memory.
